Beat together yogurt and vanilla pudding mix for 30 seconds, until moistened. Fold in powdered sugar and whipped topping until blended. Reserve 1 tablespoon vanilla crumbs and 8 mandarin oranges for topping. Layer in dessert glasses, vanilla crumbs, mandarin oranges and Bavarian cream; repeat layering. Sprinkle reserved crumbs over parfaits and top with reserved mandarin oranges.